-- Example: Admin user (password: admin_pass) - Hash: $argon2id$v=19$m=65536,t=2,p=1$uH40j24iN69WzE7V/yFfSA$tWbH/H7O9A0o6K3z1Y6B2Z/pQ5lC3p2c4m8Q2o5z2A
